                "REMOTE CONTROL T REX DINOSAUR TOYS: Roaring sounds, LED lights, fighting, dancing and more, this very cool Jurassic t-Rex dinosaur remote control toy will have any little dino enthusiast or budding paleontologist excited for a prehistoric jungle adventure or ready to rumble into a RC dinosaur battle!",
                "THRILLING RC DINOSAUR FEATURES: The Kidplokio Remote Control tyrannosaurus rex dinosaur toy has all the moves; The easy to use dinosaur footprint shaped remote control allows little ones to move their prehistoric pal forward or fast forward, enter fight mode to battle other dinosaurs or let their RC dino boogie down in dance mode!",
                "IMAGINATIVE PRETEND PLAY AWAITS: These remote control dinosaur toys are perfect for hours of Jurassic journey pretend play with family or friends or solo; the spectacular LED lights illuminate along the dinosaur’s spine, eyes and mouth, accompanied by roaring dinosaur sounds that make this RC toy all the more fun, engaging and realistic during playtime!",
                "LEARNING AND EDUCATION TOYS: Not only will your little paleontologist be thrilled and occupied for hours with this remote control dinosaur tyrannosaurus rex toy from Kidplokio, he or she will be developing and improving their hand eye coordination, dexterity and fine motor skills, while engaging in creative, fun and imaginative cosplay scenarios",
